{"tid":1261971,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch]《華爾街日報》報導:Nintendo正在醞釀Lite和Pro版本兩款Switch主機 19年聖誕上線","createTime":"2019-06-27T13:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T05:28:17.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"728974436922dcc6ddbb24c5f7cf060fb52c3669","tid":1261971,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:01:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2368104946793346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2368104946793346&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=73fb460f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2368104946793346</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npayh83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnpayh83.png&h=bf92242a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>#Nintendo新掌機或叫SwitchMini<br />\n😗#不支持連接電視 #不可拆卸手柄</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n援引《#華爾街日報》報導，Nintendo 正在醞釀兩款基於Switch的衍生版遊戲主機，並已經在東南亞投入生產，有望於2019年聖誕購物季上線。傳聞稱兩款新 Switch 主機分別為 Lite 和 Pro 版本，其中前者是價格親民的掌機版本。不過現在有越來越多的報導稱這款掌機在正式上市之後會叫做Switch Mini。<br />\n<br />\n儘管Nintendo 官方並沒有確認這款便攜式遊戲掌機的名稱，但日本遊戲主機製造商經常會選擇&ldquo;Mini&rdquo;這個後綴商標，例如SNES Classic Mini。但值得注意的是這款Mini版Switch將不會包含Switch主機的所有特性。換句話說，<strong><ins>這款設備無法連接到電視上進行遊戲，它只能作為遊戲掌機使用。因此，也不再需要可拆卸的Joy Con遊戲手柄。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n基於中國配件製造商Hon Son提供的清水套，荷蘭科技媒體LetsGoDigital渲染了2019年任天堂要推出的Switch型號。 Hon Son表示仍在等待任天堂的官方信息，因此最終設計可能會做出一些調整。儘管如此，這款清水套已經出現在其官方網站上。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wr7HVV8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWr7HVV8.png&h=5f1db54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rgh1r2O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgh1r2O.png&h=58ba8c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U6m2buu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU6m2buu.png&h=617a79dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yD4nVWa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyD4nVWa.jpg&h=c746c930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n距離任天堂 Switch Mini 的推出已經不遠了!? 從旺宏電子收到的訂單中透露端倪？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1244309/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1244309/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d5ecea9ecdf66d61b618822dc287be50dcb518ae","tid":1261971,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941da162d6303d6f8ff9060b2657b5c4333a0921","tid":1261971,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decfee66ce94c5c9f09fe023d2f3d36870e35f11","tid":1261971,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T22:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8403a53bdc4c471c53dfde6c4b9ac156aaf3cfd7","tid":1261971,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca5dbbc2bd314090c0618bf993f4cca4f2c02a8","tid":1261971,"uid":17866,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:10:22.000Z","msg":"專心出game先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無野玩出部機有撚用"},{"pid":"5ac2b37e43d6f317c928977240f2a9e81fe36eb3","tid":1261971,"uid":5320,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"aca5dbbc2bd314090c0618bf993f4cca4f2c02a8","tid":1261971,"uid":17866,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:10:22.000Z","msg":"專心出game先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無野玩出部機有撚用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src